Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受試者 Michael‧Lang
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國籍 德國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z Program 4
